🌍 Welcome to StreetSurfers


&lt;h2&gt;Discover Jakarta’s Mobility&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
  Using geospatial analytics, **StreetSurfers** dives into real-time ride-hailing data to uncover the pulse of Jakarta’s traffic system. From identifying high-demand zones to analyzing traffic bottlenecks, our platform is here to empower urban planners and policymakers.
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;
  Join us as we explore Jakarta’s traffic dynamics and pave the way for **data-driven decisions** to improve urban mobility.
&lt;/p&gt;


